click on 'Jeans' inside 'Men's' section with waiting for presence ofd element

check if 'Sort by' area is visible
scroll to 'Sort by' button and check if 'Sort by' radio is selected
check that 'Online Exclusives' radio button is not selected
click on 'Online Exclusives' checkbox
